{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/recipes/ginger-grapefruit-curd","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>I love grapefruit and one of my favorite things to do with it is to make grapefruit curd.  I put the curd on top of cookies, muffins, scones, and even fill them in little pie tins to make tarts.  I think grapefruit definitely offers a nice twist to your typical lemon curd because grapefruit has that bitterness that really adds a depth of flavor to the curd.  By the time you add your sugar - even though the bitterness is still there, it just matures the curd making it a bit more sophisticated tasting.</p>\n<p>Now, grapefruit curd is fine by itself, but I decided to add yet another twist to this.  I love mixing citrus with something spicy and ginger does just that, but in a way that is so complimenting that it makes the citrus flavor pop.</p>\n<p>Microwave grapefruit for 20 seconds for easy juicing</p>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/cb6ba37667d3d7c392489a58d150a4b8/7459a/5-2.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"5 2\" title=\"5 2\" src=\"/static/cb6ba37667d3d7c392489a58d150a4b8/7459a/5-2.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/cb6ba37667d3d7c392489a58d150a4b8/90185/5-2.jpg 450w,\n/static/cb6ba37667d3d7c392489a58d150a4b8/7459a/5-2.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<p>Grapefruit juice</p>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/3a25bd5e05737d3379286824daf2cf2a/7459a/5-3.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"5 3\" title=\"5 3\" src=\"/static/3a25bd5e05737d3379286824daf2cf2a/7459a/5-3.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/3a25bd5e05737d3379286824daf2cf2a/90185/5-3.jpg 450w,\n/static/3a25bd5e05737d3379286824daf2cf2a/7459a/5-3.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<p>Eggs, butter, sugar, zest</p>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 419px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/4c39ee1452fe4c6a82e2ae3882828fc7/1a514/5-4.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 114.55847255369929%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"5 4\" title=\"5 4\" src=\"/static/4c39ee1452fe4c6a82e2ae3882828fc7/1a514/5-4.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/4c39ee1452fe4c6a82e2ae3882828fc7/1a514/5-4.jpg 419w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 419px) 100vw, 419px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<p>Ginger powder</p>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/3df57d19491edc885fae5eff6e14d036/7459a/5-5.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"5 5\" title=\"5 5\" src=\"/static/3df57d19491edc885fae5eff6e14d036/7459a/5-5.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/3df57d19491edc885fae5eff6e14d036/90185/5-5.jpg 450w,\n/static/3df57d19491edc885fae5eff6e14d036/7459a/5-5.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<p>Double boiler for a creamy curd</p>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/73d9eea1108f817139e63e8c9c6419a9/7459a/5-6.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"5 6\" title=\"5 6\" src=\"/static/73d9eea1108f817139e63e8c9c6419a9/7459a/5-6.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/73d9eea1108f817139e63e8c9c6419a9/90185/5-6.jpg 450w,\n/static/73d9eea1108f817139e63e8c9c6419a9/7459a/5-6.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<p>Grapefruit curd ready to be jarred!</p>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/3b85d163f19350197cc4aa7a4bc90e86/7459a/5-7.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"5 7\" title=\"5 7\" src=\"/static/3b85d163f19350197cc4aa7a4bc90e86/7459a/5-7.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/3b85d163f19350197cc4aa7a4bc90e86/90185/5-7.jpg 450w,\n/static/3b85d163f19350197cc4aa7a4bc90e86/7459a/5-7.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<section class='recipe'>\n<p><strong>Recipe</strong></p>\n<p>(Makes 2 cups)                                                                           <br/>- 1 cup freshly squeezed grapefruit juice\n- 5 tablespoons unsalted butter (melted)\n- 1/4 cup sugar                               <br/>- 1/8 cup honey\n- 2 large egg yolk\n- 2 large eggs\n- 1/8 teaspoon salt\n- 2-3 tablespoon freshly squeezed lemon juice\n- 1 tablespoon ginger powder or fresh ginger juice</p>\n<p><strong>Directions</strong>\n1. Reduce grapefruit juice in sauce pan till about half cup.\n2. Whisk melted butter, sugar, salt, yolks and eggs in a glass bowl.<br/>3. Add grapefruit juice, lemon juice, and ginger juice or powder.\n4. Over a double boiler with simmering water, slowly whisk the mixture until it is thick enough to coat the back of a spoon.  The process will take about 10 minutes.  Keep a close watch on the curd so as not to cook it.\n5. Serve over your favorite cookies, muffins, scones, etc.</p></section>","timeToRead":2,"excerpt":"I love grapefruit and one of my favorite things to do with it is to make grapefruit curd.  I put the curd on top of cookies, muffins, sconesâ€¦","frontmatter":{"title":"Ginger Grapefruit Curd","image":{"feature":{"publicURL":"/static/5-1-8d8461502aa038be6db6b60526c91a8d.jpg","childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.2144212523719164,"src":"/static/8d8461502aa038be6db6b60526c91a8d/c73e5/5-1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/8d8461502aa038be6db6b60526c91a8d/00e5e/5-1.jpg 200w,\n/static/8d8461502aa038be6db6b60526c91a8d/1a903/5-1.jpg 400w,\n/static/8d8461502aa038be6db6b60526c91a8d/c73e5/5-1.jpg 640w","sizes":"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px"}}}},"feature_video":null,"date":"2014-03-03","categories":["recipes"],"tags":["recipes","sweets","grapefruit","ginger","curd"]},"fields":{"slug":"/recipes/ginger-grapefruit-curd","date":"2014-03-03T00:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/recipes/ginger-grapefruit-curd","nextslug":"/recipes/brown-butter-chocolate-chip-cookies","prevslug":"/videos/recipes/cheung-fun-noodle-roll"}}}